diff --git a/README.md b/README.md
--- a/README.md
+++ b/README.md
@@ -3,6 +3,10 @@
 `ledgerlite` is a deliberately small invoice and payment service used by the
 Garfield coordinator benchmark. It has no network or service dependencies.
 
+Payment creation requires an `Idempotency-Key`. Repeating the same key and
+payload within an account returns the original payment; changing the payload
+returns the documented conflict response.
+
